entry.title: NASA to Discuss Early Results of Artemis II Wet Dress Rehearsal
entry.published_parsed: time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=2, tm_mday=2, tm_hour=16, tm_min=40, tm_sec=1, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=33, tm_isdst=0)
entry.summary: Following a fueling test of NASA’s SLS (Space Launch System) rocket at the launch pad for the Artemis II Moon mission, leaders will discuss initial results during a news conference at 12 p.m. EST on Tuesday, Feb. 3. The agency’s SLS rocket and Orion spacecraft arrived at Launch Pad 39B at NASA’s Kennedy Space Center […]
